<collectingCountry box="[151,291,1801,1826]" name="Afghanistan" pageId="10" pageNumber="571">Afghanistan</collectingCountry>
, Kandahar - Kuna. I examined one female specimen from coll. Voss (
<collectionCode LSID="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34613" box="[1071,1152,1802,1826]" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34613" name="Zoologisches Forschungsmuseum Alexander Koenig" pageId="10" pageNumber="571">ZFMK</collectionCode>
) labeled “ 
<typeStatus box="[1264,1383,1801,1826]" pageId="10" pageNumber="571">Holotypus</typeStatus>
[red printed] / 
<taxonomicName authority="E. Voss" authorityName="E. Voss" box="[275,885,1837,1862]" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Anthomorphus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="571" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fraudulentus" subGenus="Persexarthrus">Anthomorphus (Persexarthrus) fraudulentus E. Voss</taxonomicName>
det. 
<number box="[954,1010,1837,1862]" pageId="10" pageNumber="571" value="1956.0">1956</number>
n.sp. [red asterisk] / J. Klapperich Kandahar – Kuna 
<quantity box="[373,466,1874,1898]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.2" pageId="10" pageNumber="571" unit="m" value="1200.0">1200 m</quantity>
, 
<date box="[484,553,1873,1898]" pageId="10" pageNumber="571" value="53-03-01">
<number box="[484,520,1873,1898]" pageId="10" pageNumber="571" value="1.3">1.3</number>
. 
<number box="[523,553,1873,1898]" pageId="10" pageNumber="571" value="53.0">53</number>
</date>
S-Afghanistan / 
<taxonomicName authority="Voss, 1959" authorityName="Voss" authorityYear="1959" box="[762,1224,1873,1898]" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Anthomorphus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="571" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fraudulentus">
Anthomorphus fraudulentus Voss, 
<number box="[1168,1224,1873,1898]" pageId="10" pageNumber="571" value="1959.0">1959</number>
</taxonomicName>
[folded label]”. I dissected its genitalia and added a label “Michael Košťál reprep. 
<number box="[904,965,1910,1934]" pageId="10" pageNumber="571" value="2013.0">2013</number>
”. This specimen fully corresponds to the original description and there is no doubt it is the 
<typeStatus box="[718,820,1945,1970]" pageId="10" pageNumber="571">holotype</typeStatus>
. The 
<typeStatus box="[882,980,1945,1970]" pageId="10" pageNumber="571">holotype</typeStatus>
is 
<quantity box="[1015,1116,1946,1970]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.94" pageId="10" pageNumber="571" unit="mm" value="2.94">2.94 mm</quantity>
long, completely preserved, with right elytron disjointed.
</paragraph>
